metadata.name: Elswhere #254
metadata.description:
Perlin noise walks into a Julia set and finds itself Elswhere. X is real, Y is imaginary, or is it the other way around? 

Elswhere is a unique generative art series in which noise and fractal math are combined to create whimsical shapes and motifs, with an infinite number of variations. Made with p5js.

For each pixel, the noise values corresponding to the X and Y coordinates are computed and then used as the real and imaginary components for initializing a Julia set recursion. The pixel is colored based on the number of steps it takes for the recursion to reach its base case.

Keyboard controls:
[S] Save the current view.
[2] Render 2000x3000px image.
[4] Render 4000x6000px image.
[6] Render 6000x9000px image.

Created by Elsif, 2022.05

metadata.name: Prospettive Astratte #22
metadata.description:
Architectural, volumetric perception even it it seems chaotic follow mathematical rules designed.

This generate a minimalistic volume definition fading from a single color (with different intensity and transparency) into a gray scale.

The different color grade from the beginning to the end, even on the same structure generate a different perception of the space.

By "clicking" you restart the process starting from different color, slightly different transition to gray and different levels of transparency.

Sometime volumes are very minimal and almost unperceivable, sometime, with a very bright background you want to leave the space to reveal slowly.
 
Architecture is a form of abstraction in perspective

metadata.name: DISK #110
metadata.description:
Generative art by Mark Knol (@mknol)

Abstract minimalistic composition concept. The dots on the grid are filled when connected to a disk.
Colors inspired by Piet Mondrian.

metadata.name: Highrise of Homes #221
metadata.description:
Highrise of Homes project is a "vertical community" to "accommodate people's conflicting desires to enjoy the cultural advantages of an urban center, without sacrificing the private home identity and garden space associated with suburbia."

Buy a cozy cottage in our steel constructed choice lots, less than a mile above Broadway, only ten minutes by elevator. All the comforts of the country with none of its disadvantages.

[Mouse Move]
- Zoomed View.

[Mouse Click]
- Focus/Unfocus to Zoomed View.

[r]
- Random Scene.

[s]
- At Main Screen: Save with 2200x2200 px.
- At Focused Screens: Save with window size.
